On 09/25/2012 01:37 PM, Goldfeld, Keith wrote:

>>  code<- 'Rcpp::RNGScope scope;
>
> +                    Rcpp::NumericVector rn(5);
>
> +                    for (int i=0; i<  5; i++) {
>
> +                        rn(i) = rnorm(1,0,1);
